GEANT4 simulation tools

A) Installation:
 cmake -DGeant4_DIR=$G4_BUILD10 $FOOT -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -DFILECOPY=ON
where G4_BUILD10 is the directory of builded Geant4 v10 and FOOT where the source code is located

B) Batch mode:

 1) With no flag:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -b  -out 12C_C_200.root -nev 10000 -exp 12C_200 -run 1

 2) With a given physics list:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -b  -out 12C_C_200.root -nev 10000 -exp 12C_200 -run 1 -phys [BIC, BERT or INCL]

 3) With only fragmented events:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -b  -out 12C_C_200.root -nev 10000 -exp 12C_200 -run 1 -frag

 4) With a given seed:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -b  -out 12C_C_200.root -nev 10000 -exp 12C_200 -run 1 -seed [number]

C) Interactive mode:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -exp 12C_200 -run 1

Rem: don't forget to source the data environment variables
